profile:
Welcome to Bright Edge Construction, proudly serving the Camrose and surrounding areas. Our construction crew works on residential and commercial projects, including new home projects and building construction. Specializing in Interior Services. We also do any General Contract jobs, Renovations, and Basement Development projects. We're proud to service the homes, offices, restaurants and more that serve our community.

Our services: Taping, Mudding, Suspended Ceilings, Millwork, Painting, Insulating and Drywall, Parging, Windows and Installing and Replacing, and Tilework. 


Hours of Operation Mon - Fri: 7:00 am - 6:00 pm and Sat - Sun: We are Closed
